documentation.text:
How many contracts can be paused + value for non-paused contracts + the flag index
 0 - default value for non-paused facets
 1 - paused flag
 2 - entire system
 3 - all ozTokens and wozTokens
 4 - create new tokens (factory)
 5 - OZL
